  "time_ut": 1661784933,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4\u0d9a\u0db1\u0daf\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dd8\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dba \u0dc0\u0db1\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A sand project in Mahakanadara is destroying the environment",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ambagahawela villagers say that the start of a sand treatment project on a land adjacent to the Mahakanadarava Lake Reserve has caused a lot of environmental damage.",
        "A sand purification project has been started on a land near the Mahakanadarava reservoir, adjacent to the village of Mihintale, Ambagahawela.",
        "In an inquiry about this, the Mihintale Divisional Secretariat said that an annual tax license has been issued after obtaining approval from the Irrigation Department, the Farmers Public Service Commissioner's Office, the Forest Conservation Department, the Central Environment Authority, and related institutions.",
        "Anuradhapura Irrigation Engineer Mr. Lasidu Kotwila Arachchi said that according to a complaint received from the people of that area, two officers of his company have been deployed and an investigation has been started.",
        "The Deputy Commissioner of Agricultural Services, Mr. Chaminda Ekanayake, said such an opinion when asked about this.",
        "A complaint was received from the local residents that agricultural roads and dams have been destroyed on the land near Mahakandarawa Lake Reserve. Accordingly, preliminary investigations were started. According to the report received from the officials of our company, it is reported that there has been damage. The commissioner said that the Mihintale Divisional Secretariat and the Mines and Geological Excavation Unit will be informed about it through a report."
      ],
